---
title: Seared Salmon with Lemon-Dijon Sauce plus Garlic Couscous & Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Looking for a meal that’s light and bright but still supremely satisfying? This salmon dish is all that and more. You’ll pan-sear the fillets, then place atop a bed of garlicky toasted couscous. Drizzle with a tangy mustard-lemon sauce, swirled with butter and as much zest as you please, then plate it all up with sweet roasted carrots to round out this simple, delicious dish.
